  "reference_number": "RUS1741",
  "remarks": "\nJSC LOMO is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. JSC LOMO is a Russian based entity involved in the manufacture of optical systems for weapons detection. JSC LOMO is an “involved person” per Regulations 6(2)(a)(i)&(ii) because it is or has been involved in “destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine” and “obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia” by carrying on business in the strategically important defence sector.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
